Defer is used to schedule a function call to be run after it is completed.
The function on which defer method is used, the call for the function moves to the end.

Panic is a programming error for example out of bound exception or any other exceptional condition.

Recover is used to handle run time panic.
It stops the panic and can be used to recover the value that was passed to panic.
To recover from runtime panic write a recover method inside defer statement.
